  {
    "uuid": "470ba15f-964a-57d8-875e-29a4e869ae6f",
    "entry": "休室",
    "reading": {
      "primary": "きゅうしつ",
      "alternatives": [],
      "is_heteronym": false
    },
    "grammar": {
      "pos": [
        "名詞",
        "動詞-サ変"
      ],
      "ctype": null,
      "inflections": null
    },
    "definitions": [
      {
        "index": 1,
        "gloss": "temporary closure of a room (office, exhibition, etc.)",
        "register": "standard",
        "nuance": null,
        "scenarios": [],
        "sensory_tags": {
          "colors": [],
          "temperature": null,
          "sounds": [],
          "emotions": []
        },
        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "「あ、今日の午後は職員会議で図書室が休室なんだって。放課後どこで勉強しよう？」",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "展示替えのため、来週から第3展示室は一時休室となりますので、あらかじめご了承ください。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "せっかく保健室まで来たのに、休室中の札がかかっていて、結局教室に戻るしかなかった。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "日曜・祝日は相談室を休室しております。お急ぎの方は平日の受付時間内にお電話ください。",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-3-flash-preview"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      }
    ],
